Package: vse4ts
Title: Identify Memory Patterns in Time Series Using Variance Scale Exponent
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mengyang", "Zheng", , "mengyang.zheng@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hui", "Fu", , "hui_fu@hotmail.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Methods for calculating the variance scale exponent to
    identify memory patterns in time series data. Includes tests for white
    noise, short memory, and long memory. See Fu, H. et al. (2018)
    <doi:10.1016/j.physa.2018.06.092>.
